{"tid":2379461,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"唔學盧寵茂返深圳打中國疫苗？ 梁栢賢：疫情相關工作人員與紀律部隊會獲優先接種疫苗","createTime":"2021-01-25T08:52:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T14:32:59.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"93a1a12a4437e0fadd97c230341249d631dbe6a8","tid":2379461,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:52:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572257-20210125.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572257-20210125.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABcIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=48f694c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572257-20210125.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=927d1a31\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572257-20210125.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心轄下科學委員會早前發表暫擬共識，建議接種新冠病毒疫苗的優次。新冠疫苗接種計劃專責工作小組專家成員、醫管局前行政總裁梁栢賢表示，一些與疫情有關的工作人員以及紀律部隊人員，當局會安排優先接種。<br />\n<br />\n梁栢賢在一個論壇後表示，舉例檢疫中心的工作人士、紀律部隊人員，或食環署等政府部門人員，工作也屬於高危，當局會要求各部門點算人數，再安排優先接種。他又說，也有些工種可能較高危，例如跨境司機，甚至公共運輸人員。接種次序會視乎疫苗供應及市民反應，若優先接種的市民反應不太熱烈，次優先的組別便會提前。<br />\n<br />\n另一名成員、衞生防護中心前總監曾浩輝表示，預約到接種中心注射，陪同長者的年輕照顧者也可一併接種。他說，安排是順理成章，若照顧者經常照顧長者，自己接種也有好處，可以減低長者的感染機會。<br />\n<br />\n對於當局仍未收到科興疫苗的相關數據及資料，會否考慮相同技術的其他疫苗，曾浩輝表示，沒有設下提交資料的限期，但政府也會按實際情況處理。"},{"pid":"eb97625bcf6df486bf9cd2500334f9f9664304b0","tid":2379461,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:53:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">點解保安局唔同港大深圳醫院合作<br />\n<br />\n一車車將紀律部隊車上去港大深圳醫院<br />\n<br />\n係港大深圳醫院打中國疫苗？<br />\n<br />\n仲駛乜等臨床數據，等乜等物呢？</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"63159a9f129d73d2aa6d1c1fff8a58fd6fc44a67","tid":2379461,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:53:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">李家超快D同盧寵茂合作啦<br />\n<br />\n係咪唔守城呀？ <br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9494eb2334fbefee6509a4364bfb4be3410462e9","tid":2379461,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:54:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">點解仲唔車紀律部隊家屬全家五代上去港大深圳醫院, 打中國疫苗？</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"00622e5f6d5c71bc5df0d28ee7a18a0c49277eaa","tid":2379461,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:55:08.000Z","msg":"盧寵茂打完針做逃兵無去石家莊"},{"pid":"1cdbf654bd408bce1c5a083953e8e4572b7a9744","tid":2379461,"uid":20438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:02:11.000Z","msg":"聽講 <br />\n某國疫苗第三期大規模臨床<br />\n由紀律部隊，醫護做<br />\n好多人打完未夠1星期<br />\n某國就已經話安全可以全國大規模接種<br />\n數據都未收集完就推出嚟<br />\n邊有數據拎過嚟"},{"pid":"5826d78be84e774876088ceee78829bfdd41d737","tid":2379461,"uid":321374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:08:07.000Z","msg":"3萬thx<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3bfe5c63546b38d7eac92ea2aeac83f2d91d0fe","tid":2379461,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"00622e5f6d5c71bc5df0d28ee7a18a0c49277eaa","tid":2379461,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:55:08.000Z","msg":"盧寵茂打完針做逃兵無去石家莊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:13:35.000Z","msg":"黑龍江又唔去<br />\n<br />\n石家莊又唔去<br />\n<br />\n連佐敦都唔去<br />\n<br />\n佢真係唔郁架喎"},{"pid":"3abdb322354a391ae3d0460a3da0e16787d60dc5","tid":2379461,"uid":260694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:16:12.000Z","msg":"人地去做白老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5265d197a076629f178d0737cfe8ddfda5eb339","tid":2379461,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3bfe5c63546b38d7eac92ea2aeac83f2d91d0fe","tid":2379461,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sco